rows.label: tlk42200121_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I never thought that Bahn-sama
would be such a foolish person as
to attack the summit meeting, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I hear that Bahn-sama is currently
receiving a harsh punishment
somewhere in Avaritia, mo!

rows.label: tlk42200121_05_msg0004
rows.name:
The bigger problem is that Cmalaf Artwork has
a huge stock of Bahn's woodblock prints, but
they're not selling at all anymore, mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_05_msg0005
rows.name:
With so much unsold stock,
the shop is sure to go out
of business... mo.

rows.label: tlk42200121_05_msg0006
rows.name:
The impact of Bahn-sama's downfall
is surprisingly large, mo!
